dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents municipalities for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2013. [A county wide municipal boundaries dataset.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [The municipal boundary dataset was created to fill the need for a county wide representation of the civil division boundaries. The dataset is intended for cartographic use and general spatial analysis.]
